Homepage:            http://code.haskell.org/plot
Synopsis:            GTK plots and interaction with GHCi
Description:         
     Allows use of 'plot' package with GTK
     .
     * Provides a mechanism to display and update plots from GHCi
     .

Category:            Graphics

Tested-with:         GHC==7.4.1
Cabal-version:       >= 1.8
Build-type:          Simple

